sawfowl.commandpack.api.commands.parameterized

Interface ParameterizedPlayerCommand

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.spongepowered.api.command.CommandExecutor, ParameterizedCommand, PluginCommand

    public interface ParameterizedPlayerCommand
extends ParameterizedCommand
    This interface is designed to simplify the creation of commands and add additional functionality to them.
    Commands created using this interface can only be used by players.
